{"tid":1600412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[物資組+離場賽後檢討]會繼續發夢嘅入黎","createTime":"2019-09-28T15:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T15:43:44.000Z","uid":114951,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"672c8abc8acb7bad9c6420655ad6325453857a48","tid":1600412,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪再搭黨鐵<br />\n咪亂丟低風險物資</span></strong><br />\n作為物資組有幾樣野想大家幫幫手<br />\n<strong>1. 麻煩準備離場嘅時候大家主動幫手散低風險物資<br />\n每人拎啲走</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">低風險物資包括:<br />\n普通長遮，水，生理鹽水等任何冇攻擊力/任何人都有嘅物資</span><br />\n好多時有好多有心人會買大批水/長遮<br />\n呢啲物品完全冇可疑亦都唔會比狗周<br />\n但係大批擺係到會阻住手足撤退又浪費<br />\n所以希望大家<strong>主動自發</strong>幫手散未用嘅物資<br />\n今日我見到有幾個女仔拎住十幾把長遮走冇人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>2. 麻煩呢啲低風險物資其實冇需要丟<br />\n好多有心人課好多金買</strong><br />\n見到有幾十把遮未用過就比手足放係垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>3. 如果有中等/高風險物資就盡量咪搭公共交通工具走啦<br />\n就算走避免即刻過海</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">中等風險物資包括:<br />\n頭盔眼罩豬嘴等防具</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">高風險物資包括:<br />\n任何具攻擊性/魔法師用品</span><br />\n準備定校巴/朋友接送<br />\n同埋班狗宜家次次都係隧道口截<br />\n要過海嘅朋友不妨搵定bnb酒店朋友屋企safe house住<br />\n又或者搵地方食下野飲杯野先走<br />\n如果有其他麻煩大家係下面補充<br />\n929 101再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09265ee3ff8ed6b3f803203f835753af4df24c8c","tid":1600412,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abd059999be8e3fe9aae063601c063d4072a4201","tid":1600412,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZHeBcf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZHeBcf.png&h=76b1f84f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c95ed13e617ede36351dc16c9dc79f9c9c6c2cf","tid":1600412,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c45e838cb2841141726588c69e3220c2ed46bdf1","tid":1600412,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"101港島見"},{"pid":"1478c38b6bdf11a5debb93e73798a885093fd9d8","tid":1600412,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:15:38.000Z","msg":"929遊行"},{"pid":"a2252a7d3663d4a753736e591b2dd27c7ce1633b","tid":1600412,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:16:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">準備定離場方案</span>"},{"pid":"c994bd503cf90a81da3a4cfec22c31a86b1bca3c","tid":1600412,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有高風險物資就搵定校巴啦</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c1308edd7568188d07cca754317c903c4dcbebec","tid":1600412,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32db39ee74f2412a958ea652f9a96675a095d7b1","tid":1600412,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"水好重，又容易買，拎住唔方便跑<br />\n建議放棄水樽"},{"pid":"c35f9535190956a7e4e30ec785a2937e6d2336a6","tid":1600412,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36085c850e0488997802f58282adae78e7b75d9d","tid":1600412,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"[行動POST] 10.1國慶集中討論區+TG<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600501</a>"}]}